[SIZE=5][B][COLOR=#FFD700]Why AwesomeChat?[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]

Most servers need 3-5 separate plugins to handle chat formatting, filtering, private messaging, and moderation. AwesomeChat replaces them all with one lightweight, well-integrated solution.

[LIST]
[*][B]Zero bloat[/B] - Every feature is toggleable
[*][B]Deep LuckPerms integration[/B] - Per-group everything
[*][B]Adventure API native[/B] - Full MiniMessage and hex color support
[*][B]Actively maintained[/B] for 1.19+
[/LIST]

[HR][/HR]

[SIZE=5][B][COLOR=#FFD700]Features[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Chat Formatting[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Per-group chat formats via LuckPerms
[*]Automatic prefix/suffix integration
[*]PlaceholderAPI support
[*]Hex color support ([ICODE]&#RRGGBB[/ICODE])
[*]MiniMessage formatting (toggleable)
[*]Permission-based color/style gating
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Chat Channels[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Create unlimited custom channels (staff, admin, VIP, etc.)
[*]Per-channel permission, prefix, format, and sound
[*]Toggle mode or one-off messaging
[*][ICODE]/ch join staff[/ICODE] or [ICODE]/ch staff Hello![/ICODE]
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Chat Filter Engine[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][B]Cooldown[/B] - Rate limit messages
[*][B]Spam detection[/B] - Jaro-Winkler similarity algorithm
[*][B]Banned words[/B] - Wildcard patterns from .txt files
[*][B]Anti-advertising[/B] - TLD blocking, phrase matching, domain regex
[*][B]Custom regex rules[/B] - Named rules with your own patterns
[*][B]Graduated punishments[/B] - warn -> mute -> ban per offense count
[*][B]Command filtering[/B] - Filters apply to commands too
[*][B]Violation logging[/B] - File-based logs + per-player records
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Private Messaging[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][ICODE]/msg[/ICODE], [ICODE]/reply[/ICODE], [ICODE]/whisper[/ICODE], and more
[*]Custom formats and sounds
[*]Message toggle ([ICODE]/msgtoggle[/ICODE])
[*]Social spy for staff
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Player Ignore[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][ICODE]/ignore <player>[/ICODE] - Hides their chat and blocks PMs
[*]Persistent across restarts
[*]Staff bypass permission
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Interactive Messages[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Hover text on usernames and messages
[*]Click events (suggest, execute, copy)
[*]Per-group configuration
[*]PlaceholderAPI in hover tooltips
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Moderation Tools[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][ICODE]/clearchat[/ICODE] - Clear chat (self or global)
[*][ICODE]/mutechat[/ICODE] - Toggle server-wide chat mute
[*][ICODE]/broadcast[/ICODE] - Formatted announcements with sounds
[*]Auto-broadcaster with scheduled rotating messages
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Sound System[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Per-group chat sounds
[*]Broadcast, PM, and channel sounds
[*]Configurable sound name, volume, and pitch
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Developer API[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
